<img data-src="https://gitee.com/changluJava/picture-bed/raw/master/mouse/20201122165700.png" with="60%">  

<p>取消勾选，下一步</p>
<p><img data-src="https://gitee.com/changluJava/picture-bed/raw/master/mouse/20201122165802.png">  </p>
<p>接着下一步，进行安装即可,等待完成，完成之后选择<strong>许可证</strong>进行输入：</p>
<p><code>5A02H-AU243-TZJ49-GTC7K-3C61N</code></p>
